data.description: Welcome to your luxurious retreat in Horizon's West, Winter Garden, Florida! This exceptional end unit townhouse with LAKEFRONT views of Lake Panther offers an unparalleled living experience with the master bedroom conveniently located on the main floor. As you enter, be captivated by the grandeur of the soaring 20-foot ceilings in the entryway and living room, creating an immediate sense of openness and sophistication.    The main level seamlessly blends elegance and functionality, featuring an expansive living space that effortlessly flows into the dining area and kitchen. The chef-inspired kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and abundant cabinet space, ensuring a perfect setting for culinary enthusiasts and entertaining alike.    The master bedroom, located downstairs, provides a private oasis with ample space, complemented by a lavish ensuite bathroom featuring dual sinks, oversized shower and walk-in closet. This thoughtful layout offers convenience and privacy, making it an ideal retreat.    Venture upstairs to discover an expansive loft that overlooks the breathtaking water views  This versatile space can be customized to suit your lifestyle—whether it's a home office, entertainment area, or a relaxing space to enjoy the scenic vistas, the possibilities are endless.    Step outside to your patio and relish in the Florida sunshine, surrounded by the tranquility of the community. With no rear neighbors, you can enjoy unparalleled privacy and the beauty of the natural surroundings.    Horizon's West provides a wealth of amenities, including several playgrounds, walking trails, community clubhouse, fitness center, 2 swimming pools, tennis courts, basketball courts, and community spaces. The prime location in Winter Garden ensures easy access to top-rated schools, shopping, dining, and entertainment options. Additionally, the proximity to theme parks such as Disney, Panther Lake, Hamlin Shopping Plaza, Cinepolis Luxury Cinema, Horizon West Hospital Orange County Golf Course and recreational areas makes this property a haven for leisure and family enjoyment.      Don't miss the opportunity to call this exquisite end unit townhouse home. Schedule a showing today and experience the epitome of luxury living in Winter Garden, where every detail has been thoughtfully designed to enhance your lifestyle.
